      label.col-md-3.col-form-label.font-weight-bold.text-right(for='usecaseother5') 10. If you don't have a license would you like to get one? You can do this online.
      .col-md-7
        .form-check.form-check-inline
           input(type='radio', class='form-check-input', name='usecaseother5', id='usecaseother5', value='yes')
           label.form-check-label Yes
        .form-check.form-check-inline
           input(type='radio', class='form-check-input', name='usecaseother5', id='usecaseother5', value='learn more')
           label.form-check-label I would like to learn more


    .form-group.row
      label.col-md-3.col-form-label.font-weight-bold.text-right(for='usecaseother6') 11. Would you be willing to learn how to prepare immune-boosting anti-inflammatory meals?
      .col-md-7
        .form-check.form-check-inline
           input(type='radio', class='form-check-input', name='usecaseother6', id='usecaseother6', value='yes')
           label.form-check-label Yes
