      label.col-md-3.col-form-label.font-weight-bold.text-right(for='usecaseother8') 14. If you prepare and sell 60 meals per week, you can make an estimated $1,000 per week - up to $50,000 maximum a year - by selling meals, for pick up or delivery. Your customers may include seniors, busy families, athletes and others who may be socially isolated, and individuals with health issues in your neighborhood.
      .col-md-7
        .form-check.form-check-inline
           input(type='radio', class='form-check-input', name='usecaseother8', id='usecaseother8', value='yes')
