      label.col-md-3.col-form-label.font-weight-bold.text-right(for='promotionassistance') Please this application with others who would also be interested in being trained online to become a ZIPCHEF. Or include email addresses below. We will send them a direct link. Thank you!
      .col-md-7
        input.form-control(type='email', name='reccemail', id='reccemail', placeholder='Email', autofocus, required)


